  ('dietitian-moex-08944', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '如果一個社會無法提供民眾多元的健康飲食選擇，也就是生活在一個趨胖（obesegenic）的環境中，此時 民眾處於疾病自然史的那一個階段？', '["易感受期（susceptible period）", "臨床前期（preclinical period）", "臨床期（clinical period）", "後臨床期（postclinical period）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c90dd73f29c5", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097050", "c": "113", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-08945', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '張教授提出一個酗酒與乳癌發生率的流行病學研究，從2002年開始蒐集資料，至2005年整理資料發現， 酗酒者罹患乳癌為3.5%，非酗酒者罹患乳癌為2.0%。針對此研究，下列敘述，何者正確？', '["此研究是病例對照研究法", "對比值（odds ratio）是1.75", "此研究是橫斷式研究法", "相對危險率（relative risk）是1.75"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c90dd73f29c5", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097050", "c": "113", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
